				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the director.  For the athlete, see <a href="David_Lean_(athlete)" title="David Lean (athlete)">David Lean (athlete)</a>.</div>
